snippet.title: Atelier Resleriana Official Cinematic Trailer
snippet.description:
Adventure, Alchemy, Everyday

Atelier Resleriana is a new cinematic alchemy RPG in the "Atelier" series, presented by KOEI TECMO GAMES & Akatsuki Games.

Follow all our accounts for the latest information!

Official Website: https://resleriana.atelier.games/en/
Official Atelier Resleriana X: https://twitter.com/Resleriana_EN

Pre-register for Atelier Resleriana now!

Pre-register: https://atelier-resleriana-en.onelink.me/UoA3/fjjxycoh
